EDUCATIONAL USE NOTICE:

This project is designed for educational purposes and student projects.
When using this project:

1. Always follow fire safety protocols
2. Supervise demonstrations involving fire
3. Use appropriate fire suppression equipment
4. Test in controlled environments only
5. Comply with local safety regulations
6. Get proper permissions for demonstrations

The authors and contributors are not responsible for:
- Property damage
- Personal injury
- Misuse of the project
- Violations of safety protocols
- Any damages resulting from use of this software/hardware

This is a proof-of-concept educational project. For real-world fire
suppression applications, please consult professional fire safety experts
and use certified equipment.
